text: nowpel del batobanhchea ( tondakamm) robsa yeung ban mk dl yeung kaban sangkroh sa leh ning banda anak del mean chomnue chea muoy keat daoy kdei me tda krounea ampi yeung haey( yeung ban sangkroh puokke) pi pheap ameasa robsa puokke now thngai noh . pitabrakd nasa mcheasa robsa anak mha khlangokla mha khlangpouke
